Resource Profile: CH EPREG Encounter: Mother

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-epreg/StructureDefinition/ch-epreg-encounter-mother Version: 1.0.0-ballot
Active as of 2025-05-22 Computable Name: ChEpregEncounterMother

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

This profile constrains the Encounter resource to represent a pregnancy visit from the mother's perspective.

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: CH EPREG Composition, CH EPREG Encounter: Child, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Abdominal Circumference, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Blood Pressure... Show 7 more, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Body Weight, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Fundus Height, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Gestational Age in Days, CH EPREG Observation (Base): Pregnancy Progress, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Urine Finding, CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Vagina Feature and CH EPREG Observation (Mother): Weight Gain
